00:03:21.020 --> 00:03:22.960
something else. Some people introduce

00:03:22.980 --> 00:03:24.600
things like "the triangle number of" or

00:03:24.600 --> 00:03:26.960
there's lots of combinatorial symbols that you can do,

00:03:26.960 --> 00:03:29.960
